g 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2020/06/14-768x576.jpg 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2020/06/14-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2020/06/14-440x330.jpg 440w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2020/06/14.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></figure></li></ul></figure>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:87:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2020/06/18/recap-nha-trang-wordpress-meetup-thang-6-2020/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"Nha Trang WordPress Meetup Tháng 06/2020\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2020/05/24/nha-trang-wordpress-meetup-thang-06-2020/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:86:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2020/05/24/nha-trang-wordpress-meetup-thang-06-2020/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sun, 24 May 2020 00:58:10 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Meetup\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Nha Trang\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"Nha Trang WordPress Meetup\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/?p=906\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:336:\"Xin chào tất cả mọi người, vậy là Nha Trang WordPress Meetup đã quay trở lại sau nhiều tháng gián đoạn bởi dịch bệnh COVID-19, lần này Ban tổ chức sẽ mang đến cho toàn thể các bạn yêu mến WordPress tại Nha Trang các chủ đề hấp dẫn như sau. Xin chào tất cả [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Dat Hoang\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6612:\"\n<p>Xin chào tất cả mọi người, vậy là Nha Trang WordPress Meetup đã quay trở lại sau nhiều tháng gián đoạn bởi dịch bệnh COVID-19, lần này Ban tổ chức sẽ mang đến cho toàn thể các bạn yêu mến WordPress tại Nha Trang các chủ đề hấp dẫn như sau.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2020/05/Copy-of-nha-trang-wordpres-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-911\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2020/05/Copy-of-nha-trang-wordpres-1024x576.png 1024w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2020/05/Copy-of-nha-trang-wordpres-300x169.png 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2020/05/Copy-of-nha-trang-wordpres-768x432.png 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2020/05/Copy-of-nha-trang-wordpres-1536x864.png 1536w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2020/05/Copy-of-nha-trang-wordpres.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<span id=\"more-906\"></span>\n\n\n\n<p>Xin chào tất cả mọi người, vậy là Nha Trang WordPress Meetup đã quay trở lại sau nhiều tháng gián đoạn bởi dịch bệnh COVID-19, lần này Ban tổ chức sẽ mang đến cho toàn thể các bạn yêu mến WordPress tại Nha Trang các chủ đề hấp dẫn như sau</p>\n\n\n\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4f/2/16/1f3af.png\" alt=\"&#x1f3af;\"> <strong>Topic dự kiến:</strong><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tf0/2/16/1f449.png\" alt=\"&#x1f449;\"> Tối Ưu Tốc Độ WordPress trên VPS với Cache Disk &#8211; RAM<br>Trình bày: Mr. Minh Nguyễn | CEO Minh Duy Solutions</p>\n\n\n\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tf0/2/16/1f449.png\" alt=\"&#x1f449;\"> Tối Ưu Điểm Google Pagespeed Insight (Dự kiến)<br>Trình bày: Mr. Quyền Lê | CEO Bignet Solutions</p>\n\n\n\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4f/2/16/1f3af.png\" alt=\"&#x1f3af;\"> <strong>Thời gian:</strong><br>09h00 &#8211; 11h30 ngày 06/06/2020 (GMT +7)</p>\n\n\n\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4f/2/16/1f3af.png\" alt=\"&#x1f3af;\"><strong> Địa điểm:</strong><br>TOONG coworking space Nha Trang (Dự kiến)<br>Số 1 Trần Hưng Đạo, Lộc Thọ, Thành phố Nha Trang</p>\n\n\n\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4f/2/16/1f3af.png\" alt=\"&#x1f3af;\"> <strong>Đăng ký tham dự:</strong><br><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FVnzCdMfjnQNknb1R8%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1JnwDgxhquL1EehsksX3ynE8hB_ADWcRz4wt89dhqH_vB4UkTubNbS6xo&amp;h=AT1uncA47tvtL51iemZh4bzPyXTNjLzYM4M5PZKOpUwY1eTovkfG03DEkf9n3_A2i5pZqS6Wh4YGCO-KGy8hOOgHxSwa_8tMB_i0v-jUSDX10mi92Fq4DVHDTG0veIDJL96h_Q9n-KuP3daMEDYR13Qdeg\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/VnzCdMfjnQNknb1R8</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4f/2/16/1f3af.png\" alt=\"&#x1f3af;\"> <strong>Các kênh truyền thông khác:</strong><br>&#8211; WordPress.Org:<br><a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2020/05/24/nha-trang-wordpress-meetup-thang-06-2020\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https://vi.wordpress.org/2020/05/24/nha-trang-wordpress-meetup-thang-06-2020</a><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvi.wordpress.org%2F2020%2F05%2F24%2Fnha-trang-wordpress-meetup-thang-06-2020%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR27MNanH-fAebmdu8OomxYFpOXF3FqoHOlEiVFAD0GMPHoi5cdtKqx1KL4&amp;h=AT3Dwt88CHTuZCf5_f7ptXWpZ8Xl8OCsWXXkj0RspvhoDBibpcZ4RnTR_dkZ1oWJ-m18rFWV4tMCT0-0ujmQnKmtGa4oeMsEr5GHC2U17hjzE9pntG6hEnuhRoxEOSDOmK_mD0qKbkAW0TQ-K_yMqex90A\" target=\"_blank\">/</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8211; Meetup.com:<br><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Nha-Trang-WordPress/events/270829975/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https://www.meetup.com/Nha-Trang-WordPress/events/270829975/</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4f/2/16/1f3af.png\" alt=\"&#x1f3af;\"><strong> Quà tặng:</strong><br>&#8211; Hosting Miễn Phí của Minh Duy Solutions<br>&#8211; Dịch Vụ Tối Ưu Website của Bignet Solutions</p>\n\n\n\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4f/2/16/1f3af.png\" alt=\"&#x1f3af;\"> <strong>Cám ơn đơn vị tài trợ địa điểm:</strong><br>Xin trân trọng cám ơn <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/toonggoldcoast/\">TOONG coworking space</a> đã nhiệt tình tài trợ địa điểm meetup cho Nha Trang WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4f/2/16/1f3af.png\" alt=\"&#x1f3af;\"> <strong>FAQ:</strong><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tf0/2/16/1f449.png\" alt=\"&#x1f449;\"> Nha Trang WordPress Meetup là hoạt động offline hàng tháng nhằm phát triển cộng đồng yêu thích và sử dụng WordPress tại Nha Trang<br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tf0/2/16/1f449.png\" alt=\"&#x1f449;\"> Nha Trang WordPress Meetup là LOCAL GROUP chính thức được công nhận bởi <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2FWordPress.Org%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR22nDiBscIykqI-wiz6YFCEtaGxhfsTOEAvo3Hi7cK6Pkhw_kfgHuKHa40&amp;h=AT1YIdx--ed9EIcJfuTZnXxibVFSaWO2QOSKT4g2mLHh-qp9UL02SAbWCdDvjyh0RPYzJ6fzC1ANh2Zy8kpmFBVMbk5HZ736JVXq-DKSERxRQrRrqyvmHO9MABQmxanlI3y6yk5VxRUvQxpwsN9FLTlJBQ\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress.Org</a> hoạt động từ năm 2016.<br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tf0/2/16/1f449.png\" alt=\"&#x1f449;\"> Nha Trang WordPress Meetup là chương trình hoàn toàn miễn phí, không thu phí vào cổng đối với người tham gia (Trừ một số trường hợp hỗ trợ Ban tổ chức thuê địa điểm tổ chức)</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2020/05/24/nha-trang-wordpress-meetup-thang-06-2020/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"5\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:35:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/news/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"\n	hourly	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"\n	1	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:8:{s:6:\"server\";s:5:\"nginx\";s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Sat, 09 Jul 2022 10:10:02 GMT\";s:12:\"content-type\";s:34:\"application/rss+xml; charset=UTF-8\";s:6:\"x-olaf\";s:3:\"⛄\";s:13:\"last-modified\";s:29:\"Sat, 18 Jun 2022 04:29:08 GMT\";s:4:\"link\";s:61:\"<https://vi.wordpress.org/wp-json/>; rel=\"https://api.w.org/\"\";s:15:\"x-frame-options\";s:10:\"SAMEORIGIN\";s:4:\"x-nc\";s:9:\"HIT ord 1\";}}s:5:\"build\";s:14:\"20211220193300\";}